_sText:
I have make my Gun Game Map "gg_sandstorm" to a Fight Yard Map. On the middle upper Wall i have put a AK'47, and in the Bunker a M4A1. At the Big Boxes in the upper Area can you take Grenades.  I have put 2 Item Boxes they drop a HE Grenade if you open it. The Map is Dust like. I think the Map is good for Fight Yard. I have put the Player Spawns all over the Map not at 1 Position. The Map has a upper and a down Area. At the down Area you can go to a third Area with a Scud Launch Field. Have Fun

our skillor
